+       depends on EFI && !X86_USE_3DNOW && (!XEN || XEN_BZIMAGE)
+       select RELOCATABLE if !XEN
        ---help---
           This kernel feature allows a bzImage to be loaded directly
 	  by EFI firmware without the use of a bootloader.
